uk.co.saiman.msapex.data

Interface AnnotationHandler<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the annotation to be handled by this handler

    public interface AnnotationHandler<T>
    An annotation handler applies to all annotation of its type. It translates a conceptual annotation into an UI representation.
